## Step Functions Flow

```
Start
 ↓
Ingest Bronze
 ↓
Process Silver
 ↓
Update Gold
 ↓
Refresh Mart
 ↓
End
```

---

# 🧱 Passo 10 — Atualizar Data Mart

Gold alimenta marts.

Exemplo:

```sql
CREATE TABLE lakehouse.mart_carteira
WITH (
    format='PARQUET',
    external_location='s3://lakehouse/mart/cobranca/dashboard/'
)
AS
SELECT
    data_snapshot,
    SUM(saldo) saldo_total
FROM lakehouse.gold_carteira
GROUP BY data_snapshot;
```

---

# 🧱 Passo 11 — Conectar QuickSight

Dataset:

```
Athena
 ↓
mart_carteira
```

Sempre consumir **mart ou gold**.

Nunca Bronze.

